14. **From Eq. (8.46) and the inequalities among the components $$ h_{\alpha \beta} $$, derive Eqs. (8.47) – (8.50).**

    Eq. (8.47) is from Eq. (8.30) and the fact that $$ \bar{h}{0 0} $$ is the dominating term is from Eq. (8.42).

