    b.  **The general solution to the equation $$ \nabla^2 f = g $$, which vanishes at infinity, is the generalization of Eq. (8.2),**

        $$ f(x) = - \frac{1}{4 \pi} \int \frac{g(y)}{| x - y |} \mathrm{d}^3 y, $$

